-- Lemma1/Summability.lean: Proof of Covariance Series Summability
--
-- This file completes Step 2 of Lemma 1: proving that the covariance series
-- converges using the lag_regroup_identity from Proofs/LagRegroupProof.
--
-- Mathematical Content:
--   Γ(y,z) = Σ_{d=0}^∞ γ_d(y,z) < ∞
--   where γ_d(y,z) = Cov(Y₁(y), Y_{1+d}(z)) is the lag-d autocovariance.
--
-- Proof Strategy:
--   1. Use lag_regroup_identity to organize double sums by lag
--   2. Apply Davydov's inequality to bound each γ_d by α(d)
--   3. Use AlphaMixing.summable to conclude convergence
--
-- STATUS: Framework complete - uses axioms where full proofs require
--        probability/dependence structure beyond current Mathlib

