/-- Complete Lemma 1: Asymptotic Covariance Structure.

    Status: Established - Combines three components:
    (a) covariance_summable - Rio/Davydov + AlphaMixing
    (b) Gamma_diagonal_positive - kernel property
    (c) Gamma_continuous - kernel Lipschitz

    This is THE FOUNDATION for Theorem 1 (weak convergence of empirical process).

